EDIT: I have turned off the comments because I havent had any new prompts in a few weeks. This way I can export the comments once and not miss any. Thanks for all the prompts!
-
With all the buzz around #aiart I want to try something.
-
Instead of using an A.I. Art generator, write your prompt in the comments and I promise, I'll draw every single prompt this year. It won't be as fast, but it will be made by me, a Human.
-
I have found that I am a little uninspired of late and I need to play in my sketchbook a little more, so I would love some random prompts to help jumpstart my creative process. your prompt can be a single word, a precise description, or a collection of random unrelated words. I can't wait to see what you all suggest. I'll tag you when I publish your prompt so you won't miss. Please share around so I can get as many suggestions as possible.
-
All NSFW comments will be deleted.
-
-
-
-
-
#noaiart #aiartprompts #iamnotarobot #makeart #makecomics #indiecomics
